_sText: Gg_deathroom is basically a map which contains triggers. once a player has stepped on a trigger they will be teleported into the deathroom. in the deathroom there is no escape and only other players can open the doors form the outside. other features of the map include exploding the deathroom and flooding the entire map. i hope you enjoy my third release =) i have also .bz2 all the required files for you convenience
